extends layout

block content
  h1 Home
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary++], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.
  h3 Stats
  p The library has the following record counts:
  ul
    li #[strong Books:] !{ bookCount }
    li #[strong Copies:] !{ bookInstanceCount }
    li #[strong Copies available:] !{ bookInstanceAvailableCount }
    li #[strong Authors:] !{ authorCount }
    li #[strong Genres:] !{ genreCount }
